{This is a companion hand to Deal 13.

WEST has 14 points, the same strength she had in Deal 13. But what a difference. 
This time EAST's \S shortness complements her hand very well. She bids 4\C 
to show her Control, and after EAST shows the \DA she 
uses Blackwood to make sure EAST also has the trump Ace.}

